snippet.title: Dungeon Raid Gameplay
snippet.description: This shows the iPhone puzzle/RPG game Dungeon Raid, in the early stages of a game while the character has no skills and with beginner items. As you collect tiles, you can upgrade your character's stats & skills, as well as buy & upgrade items, and fight off the constant threat of enemy (skull) tiles. Check it out in App Store: http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/dungeon-raid/id403090531?mt=8
